metadata.name: Biomechanical Goddess #5
metadata.description:
In those moments when you're choking on despair, when you feel like you can't do anything and that it's impossible to do anything, just know that only in those moments do you truly move forward.

You see how her eyelashes are trembling!!!  
Everything in this life is for a reason! My Biomechanical Goddesses teach me to love this world and see only good things
